    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯与菲律宾讨论南海‘威慑’</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/hegseth-discusses-south-china-sea-deterrence-with-philippines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对南海地缘政治紧张局势，美国国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯在与马尼拉国防部长通话时重申了华盛顿对与菲律宾建立共同防御条约的“坚定”承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/hegseth-discusses-south-china-sea-deterrence-with-philippines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 05:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国援助冻结导致刚果救援工作放缓，尸体在街头腐烂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-aid-freeze-slows-relief-in-congo-as-bodies-rot-in-streets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府冻结了几乎所有的外国援助，这妨碍了对刚果民主共和国东部人道主义危机的充分响应，上周该地的战斗造成近 3,000 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-aid-freeze-slows-relief-in-congo-as-bodies-rot-in-streets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 05:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理通过预算案 但尚不清楚他能做更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/france-s-premier-passed-a-budget-but-it-s-unclear-he-can-do-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁 (Francois Bayrou) 强行通过了法国分裂议会的预算案，并成功阻止了极左翼势力推翻其政府的企图。但他的连胜纪录可能就此结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/france-s-premier-passed-a-budget-but-it-s-unclear-he-can-do-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
